AngloGold, Thani to Accelerate Exploration at the Hodine Prospect in Egypt

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-04-20T09:46:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-20/anglogold-thani-to-accelerate-exploration-at-the-hodine-prospect-in-egypt.html
AngloGold Ashanti Ltd. (ANG)  said its
joint venture with Thani Emirates Resource Holdings in the
Middle East and North Africa plans to accelerate exploration at
the Hodine prospect in  Egypt  after finding “potentially
significant gold mineralization” there.  AngloGold commented in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  